48:39.149 --> 48:41.982
- You didn't like it?
- I like it very much.

48:42.619 --> 48:44.348
But, Tony, come on.

48:45.022 --> 48:47.923
You're a nice guy,
but I got my own problems.

48:47.991 --> 48:50.289
